#encoding: utf-8

Feature: Literals1 - Boolean and Null

  Scenario: [1] Return a boolean true lower case
    Given any graph
    When executing query:
      """
      RETURN true AS literal
      """
    Then the result should be, in any order:
      | literal |
      | true    |
    And no side effects

